WEBVTT

00:04:28.565 --> 00:04:30.895
Els amics em deien:
"James, vols quedar?"

00:04:30.895 --> 00:04:33.195
I jo: "No puc,
espero un correu sobre l'or."

00:04:34.041 --> 00:04:36.085
Vaig concloure que ja n'hi havia prou.

00:04:36.085 --> 00:04:38.109
Havia d'acabar-ho, rídiculament.

00:04:38.109 --> 00:04:39.343
Vaig traçar un pla.

00:04:39.343 --> 00:04:41.197
Li vaig dir: "Mira, Solomon,

00:04:41.197 --> 00:04:42.771
estic preocupat per la seguretat.

00:04:42.791 --> 00:04:43.822
Quan ens escrivim,

00:04:43.822 --> 00:04:45.333
hem de fer servir un codi."

00:04:45.333 --> 00:04:48.277
(Rialles)

00:04:48.582 --> 00:04:49.733
Hi va estar d'acord.

00:04:49.757 --> 00:04:50.899
(Rialles)

00:04:50.899 --> 00:04:52.339
I vaig dir: "Solomon, he estat

00:04:52.339 --> 00:04:54.419
tota la nit pensant 
i he creat aquest codi.

00:04:54.419 --> 00:04:56.547
A partir d'ara l'hem de fer servir:

00:04:56.547 --> 00:04:59.880
Advocat: Osset de goma.